text: NakedJen is now on "Clubhouse". To Jen, some people are on all the time. I'm not one of them, at least not yet. But I want to hang out with you, so if you want to chat with me, send me a ping. Best way is to start a room, and click + and invite me. I'll get notification on my phone. I may not show up. That's the protocol. Love that you're there!
